.jumbotron
  %h1 Welcome to Pibble.co
  %p
    Pibble is a curation of products we’ve bought for our 3 year old rescue pebble, Molly, over the last year and a half.  We’ve only listed the products we’ve bought and love and provided explanations for why we like them and why we think you and your pitty will too.

- @products.each do |p|
  .products.col-sm-6.col-md-4
    %a{ href: product_path(p) }
      .thumbnail
        %img{src: p.product_image_url(:thumb).to_s }
          .caption
            %h3
              = p.name
            %p
              %button.btn.btn-lg.btn-success{:disabled => "disabled", :type => "button"}
                %span.badge $#{p.price}
                on Amazon
